---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Badge from '@/components/ui/Badge.astro';

const updated = 'June 23, 2026';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="How ctrlaltorion.com handles data, cookies, newsletter sign-ups, and third-party advertising (Google AdSense)."
>
  <div class="pt-32 pb-24 px-6">
    <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <Badge tag="legal" />
      <h1 class="font-display text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold text-cream leading-tight mt-6 mb-4">
        Privacy<br />Policy.
      </h1>
      <p class="font-mono text-xs text-muted mb-12">Last updated: {updated}</p>

      <div class="space-y-4 text-muted leading-relaxed [&_h2]:font-display [&_h2]:text-2xl [&_h2]:font-bold [&_h2]:text-cream [&_h2]:mt-12 [&_h2]:mb-3 [&_a]:text-violet [&_a:hover]:text-cream [&_a]:underline [&_a]:underline-offset-2 [&_ul]:list-disc [&_ul]:pl-6 [&_ul]:space-y-2 [&_strong]:text-cream [&_strong]:font-medium">
        <p class="text-cream text-lg leading-relaxed">
          This Privacy Policy explains how Ctrl Alt Orion LLC (&ldquo;we,&rdquo; &ldquo;us,&rdquo; or
          &ldquo;our&rdquo;) collects, uses, and protects information when you visit
          <strong>ctrlaltorion.com</strong> (the &ldquo;Site&rdquo;). By using the Site, you agree to
          the practices described below.
        </p>

        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We aim to collect as little personal information as possible. Depending on how you interact with the Site, this may include:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Information you provide directly.</strong> If you subscribe to our newsletter or contact us, we collect the email address and any message content you submit.</li>
          <li><strong>Information collected automatically.</strong> Like most websites, our servers and service providers may log standard technical data such as your IP address, browser type, device information, referring pages, and the dates and times of your visits.</li>
          <li><strong>Cookies and similar technologies.</strong> We and our third-party partners use cookies and similar technologies as described below.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>How We Use Information</h2>
        <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Operate, maintain, and improve the Site;</li>
          <li>Send you our newsletter or respond to your inquiries, where you have requested it;</li>
          <li>Monitor and analyze usage and trends to improve your experience;</li>
          <li>Detect, prevent, and address technical issues, fraud, or abuse; and</li>
          <li>Comply with legal obligations.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Cookies</h2>
        <p>Cookies are small text files stored on your device. We use them to keep the Site functioning and to understand how it is used. You can set your browser to refuse cookies or to alert you when cookies are being sent; however, some parts of the Site may not function properly if you disable them.</p>

        <h2>Advertising &amp; Third-Party Vendors</h2>
        <p>We use third-party advertising companies, including <strong>Google</strong>, to serve ads when you visit the Site.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Third-party vendors, including Google, use cookies to serve ads based on your prior visits to this and other websites.</li>
          <li>Google&rsquo;s use of advertising cookies enables it and its partners to serve ads to you based on your visit to this Site and/or other sites on the Internet.</li>
          <li>You may opt out of personalized advertising by visiting <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Ads Settings</a>.</li>
          <li>You may also opt out of some third-party vendors&rsquo; use of cookies for personalized advertising by visiting <a href="https://www.aboutads.info/choices/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">aboutads.info</a> or <a href="https://www.youronlinechoices.eu/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">youronlinechoices.eu</a>.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>For more information about how Google uses data when you use our Site, see <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google&rsquo;s policy</a>.</p>

        <h2>Analytics</h2>
        <p>We use Google Analytics to help us understand how visitors use the Site. It collects aggregated, non-identifying usage data and is governed by <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google&rsquo;s Privacy Policy</a>. You can opt out using the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on</a>.</p>

        <h2>How We Share Information</h2>
        <p>We do not sell your personal information. We share information only with service providers who help us operate the Site (such as hosting, email delivery, analytics, and advertising partners), and only as needed to provide those services, or when required by law.</p>

        <h2>Data Retention</h2>
        <p>We retain personal information, such as newsletter sign-ups, for as long as needed to provide the service you requested or until you ask us to delete it. You can unsubscribe at any time using the link in any newsletter email, or by contacting us.</p>

        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>Depending on your location, you may have the right to access, correct, or delete the personal information we hold about you, or to object to certain processing. To exercise these rights, contact us using the details below.</p>

        <h2>Children&rsquo;s Privacy</h2>
        <p>The Site is not directed to children under 13, and we do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you believe a child has provided us with personal information, please contact us and we will delete it.</p>

        <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. When we do, we will revise the &ldquo;Last updated&rdquo; date at the top of this page. Continued use of the Site after changes take effect constitutes acceptance of the revised policy.</p>

        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, contact us at <a href="mailto:mitchell@ctrlaltorion.com">mitchell@ctrlaltorion.com</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
